:: About Project {"position":"100,200","size":"100,100"}
This is a prototype storytelling project, developed at the PeaceTech Hackathon in March 2024 with collaboration of a small but diverse group of people who are engaged in humanitarian project and digital media. Our goal is to raise awareness, and support Digital Literacy for Prevention through interactive media. This is a storybook made with the open source Twine (twinery.org) tool, that could be translated or used in various formats.

