:: Ata's Story {"position":"275,275","size":"100,100"}
In the small village where Rohingya families lived in Myanmar, there was a young man named Ata Tun. His opportunities to develop were limited due to his lack of citizenship status, which meant he could not attend school or work legally. Political instability and lack of economic prospects led him down a dark path, that he would later come to regret.

<img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/BJeQzeQiap.jpg" width="100%">

