:: First Target {"position":"450,625","size":"100,100"}
Ata Tun's first victim was a young girl named Huma. She had dreams of going to school but knew the odds were stacked against her. When she met Ata online, she saw him as an opportunity for friendship and support. Little did she know that he would use their relationship to exploit her in unimaginable ways.

[[Read Huma's Story->Huma's Story]]

